  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/ed4a6cdf0babfdaa63fa048de3d9b8d0a4c06522" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.801ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \mathbf {1} _{A}}"></span> defined by <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \mathbf {1} _{A}\!(x)=1}">
