</p><p>The indicator function of <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">A</span> is the <a href="/wiki/Iverson_bracket" title="Iverson bracket">Iverson bracket</a> of the property of belonging to <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">A</span>; that is, 
</p><p><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \mathbf {1} _{A}(x)=\left[\ x\in A\ \right].}">
